==Bandwagon==

URL = http://bandwagon.io/

"Bandwagon, Mahfouda’s new ride-share service that launched at LaGuardia Airport in July, fills underutilized capacity in taxis by matching passengers who have complementary destinations and getting them into the same cab. Drivers make a better fare, passengers pay less for the same distance they would travel alone, and the idea, if it catches on, will likely amount to enormous environmental advantages over time." 
(http://onthecommons.org/magazine/taxi-rides-go-communal)


